## 🏗️ IMMUTABLE ARCHITECTURE RULES

- **Strict MVC**:
  - Controllers: `app/Http/Controllers/` (Extend BaseController)
  - Models: `app/Models/` (Use Prepared Statements)
  - Views: `app/views/pages/` (.php ONLY, No Blade)
  - Routes: `routes/web.php`
- **Zero Duplicate Policy**: Naya file banane se pehle check karo. Agar file exist karti hai, toh use `smart-editing-no-duplicates.md` ke mutabik edit/enhance karo.

## 🗄️ DATABASE & XAMPP STANDARDS

- **Connection**: MySQL `root` user (no password) on localhost.
- **Schema Guardian**: 610 tables ka logic break na ho, isliye har query se pehle `mysql` tool se table structure verify karo.
- **Optimization**: Har query ko `EXPLAIN` karo. Agar execution time >100ms hai, toh autonomously index add karo.

## 🛡️ SAFETY & CLEANUP PROTOCOL

- **Backup First**: Core `config/` ya framework files edit karne se pehle `.bak` version banao.
- **Safe Migration**: Purane legacy code ko delete mat karo. Use extract karke MVC mein dalo aur purani file ko `_DEPRECATED/` folder mein shift karo.
- **Security Shield**: Har input ko SQLi aur XSS se sanitize karne ke liye middleware use karo.

## 🐙 TOOL INTEGRATION & MONITORING

- **GitKraken**: Har bug fix ya module complete hone par atomic commit karo. Format: `[Auto-Fix] <scope>: <action]`.
- **Puppeteer**: Frontend change ke baad UI verify karo. 404/500 errors ko turant fix karo.
- **Dashboard**: Har cycle ke baad `monitoring_dashboard.html` update karo taaki progress dikhti rahe.

